{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d3fa59d8e3","title":"鸣放反动言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"56970476a4","index":0,"year":1957,"month":10,"day":21,"articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"36c83c8b4b","name":"宗教界人士"},{"id":"3af02c0659","name":"江西"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"522f1bd5cc","type":"title","text":"鸣放反动言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"b900ca5c4d","type":"authors","text":"江西宗教界人士","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"dc29e6bc86","type":"subtitle","text":"江西省宗教界人士学习班学员鸣放出的十五点反动言论","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"c196a2a2be","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社南昌16日讯　由江西省人委办公厅举办的江西省宗教界人士学习班已在10月21日正式开始学习，预计两个月结束。参加学习的有来自全省各重点市县的天主教、基督教神职人员和部分教徒一百零九人。学习期间准备分四个阶段：第一阶段是安定情绪，学习文件；第二阶段是鸣放；第三阶段是批判、辩论；最后阶段是总结。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"197362d566","type":"paragraph","text":"现在已由鸣放转到批判、辩论阶段。神职人员和教徒在鸣放中“放”出的反动言论大致可分为十五点：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"cc2f3d191f","type":"paragraph","text":"1．社会主义是铁幕，没有民主自由，给人民带来灾难和痛苦。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"0dcd8c6b29","type":"paragraph","text":"2．爱国会是傀儡组织，是共产党插在宗教内的一把刀子。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"6fa598e286","type":"paragraph","text":"3．爱国会是叛教、裂教，是脱离教皇的组织。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"3daf0f6612","type":"paragraph","text":"4．教会里没有帝国主义和反革命分子，肃反运动把人民内部矛盾扩大为敌我矛盾。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"9e514cf458","type":"paragraph","text":"5．无神论与有神论者水火不相容，宗教与社会主义无法共存。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"49232536c0","type":"paragraph","text":"6．不能拥护共产党和社会主义，如拥护了就是承认唯物主义，承认它就是反对自己。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"c21bb4769a","type":"paragraph","text":"7．宁可失天下，不可失灵魂。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"06afef42ff","type":"paragraph","text":"8．圣母军不是反动的，是共产党在报上渲染的。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"8b4b1aa529","type":"paragraph","text":"9．公教与非公教的人不能在一起辩论。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"6bcaccd4a1","type":"paragraph","text":"10．梵蒂冈不是帝国主义，因它不是独立国，要坚决跟它走，不要与它割断政治、经济联系。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"81ff8d5776","type":"paragraph","text":"11．承认中国有两个政府：北京政府和台湾政府。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"9af70d866d","type":"paragraph","text":"12．爱国不分新中国与旧中国。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"919534c5d7","type":"paragraph","text":"13．半个社会主义论：承认社会主义建设，不承认共产党领导宗教。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"374681975b","type":"paragraph","text":"14．爱国会的进步领导是封建把头，是政府的狗腿子。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"8d291bda7d","type":"paragraph","text":"15．教宗通论是给中国教友的警惕。(董瑛)","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"},{"id":"401e5206ff","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：新华社《内部参考》1957年11月20日。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3"}],"page":{"id":"505e14c3e8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3fa59d8e3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}